- [Alco.Editor.csproj](mdc:Editor/Alco.Editor/Alco.Editor.csproj)

# The naming rule of the x:Name in axaml UI

- Button: Start with "Btn". For example: "BtnConfirm", "BtnCancel"
- Event: Start with "On", also end with "Click" if it is a button event. For example: "OnRefresh", "OnBtnConfirmClick"
- Text: Start with "Text", for example. For example: "TextTitle"